Package: rapid.spreadsheets
Type: Package
Title: Create reproducible and accessible spreadsheets
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Hannah", "Bunk", role = "aut"),
    person("Patrycja", "Delong-Smith", role = "aut"),
    person("Emyr", "John", role = "aut"),
    person("Steve", "Reynolds", role = "aut"),
    person("RAPID team", email = "DASCH_RAPID@ons.gov.uk", role = "cre"),
    person("Office for National Statistics", role = c("cph", "fnd")))
Maintainer: RAPID team <DASCH_RAPID@ons.gov.uk>
Description: rapid.spreadsheets can help you automate production of
    spreadsheets that follow accessibility guidelines outlined in:
    <https://analysisfunction.civilservice.gov.uk/policy-store/releasing-statistics-in-spreadsheets/>
    It supports creating reference tables that can include: Cover sheet,
    Contents table, Notes table and Data tables. Aside from data tables, all
    sheet types support use of internal and external hyperlinks. As
    rapid.spreadsheets package was built using openxlsx workbooks it provides
    users with flexibility to add and modify formatting styles using openxlsx
    functions.
